Develop Wordpress Site for Machine Learning Startup

-----------------------------
We are a machine learning startup

What we're looking for:
An experienced web dev with to create a new wordpress site for us. We have nearly pixel perfect designs done in Sketch but just need a web developer to implement them. 

Deliverables:

1. To start, we just want one page done using just HTML and CSS. 
2. After that, we will have 5-10 other pages that need to be implemented in Wordpress. You can see the page in the attachment. 
